BUGGYCOMMIT.MESSAGE: Add min_over_time (#127649) This change adds support for `min_over_time` in time-series data streams. Similar to `max_over_time`, `min_over_time` is translated to compute the min per time-series first. For example: ``` TS my-metrics | STATS SUM(min_over_time(memory_usage)) BY cluster, bucket(@timestamp, 1 minute) ``` is translated into: ``` TS my-metrics | STATS min_memory_usage=min(memory_usage), cluster=VALUES(cluster) BY _tsid, ts=bucket(@timestamp, 1 minute) | STATS sum(min_memory_usage) BY cluster, ts ```
